      "comment": "REGAL REBA (2) failed to threaten in two average runs to date. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Has ability and is a key runner. RATBAG RUBY (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.80) last time in a Maiden at this track. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Worth another chance. CASH CARRIAGE (1) is yet to break through in eight starts but has run a number of placings. Returns to favourable course after finishing fifth (18.02) at Murray Bridge Straight latest. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Expected to run well. PHOTO CRUSHER (8) will make his presence felt on the back of recent top-three finishes.",
